trans-unit.source: Represents an individual row in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en enkelt rad i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The GridViewRow class is used represent an individual row in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen GridViewRow brukes representere en enkelt rad i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: Each row in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control has a designated row type using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlRowType> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Hver rad i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen har en bestemt rad typen ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlRowType>opplisting.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlRowType> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: The following table lists the different row types.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser annen radtyper.

trans-unit.source: |Row type|Description| |--------------|-----------------| |`DataRow`|A data row in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.| |`EmptyDataRow`|The empty row in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.
trans-unit.target: | Radtypen | Beskrivelse | |--------------|-----------------| | `DataRow`| En datarad <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollens. | | `EmptyDataRow`| Raden i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: The empty row is displayed when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control has no records to display and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.EmptyDataTemplate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> template is not `null`.| |`Footer`|The footer row in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.| |`Header`|The header row in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.| |`Pager`|A pager row in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.| |`Separator`|A separator row in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.| To determine the row type of a GridViewRow object, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.RowType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den tomme raden vises når kontrollen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>har ingen poster for visning ikke og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.EmptyDataTemplate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>malen `null`. | | `Footer`| Bunntekstraden i kontrollen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>. | | `Header`| Overskriftsraden <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollens. | | `Pager`| En personsøker rad <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollens. | | `Separator`| En rad skilletegn i kontrollen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>. | Bruk til å fastslå rad objekttypen en GridViewRow den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.RowType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.RowType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.EmptyDataTemplate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: A GridViewRow object also has a state associated with it.
trans-unit.target: En GridViewRow-objektet har også en tilstand som er knyttet til den.

trans-unit.source: The state can be a bitwise combination of the values in the following table.
trans-unit.target: Tilstanden kan være en bitvis kombinasjon av verdier i tabellen nedenfor.

trans-unit.source: |State value|Description| |-----------------|-----------------| |`Alternate`|The GridViewRow object is an alternate row in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.| |`Edit`|The GridViewRow object is in edit mode.| |`Normal`|The GridViewRow object is in its normal (default) state.| |`Selected`|The GridViewRow object is selected.| To determine the state of a GridViewRow object, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.RowState%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: | Angi verdien | Beskrivelse | |-----------------|-----------------| | `Alternate`| GridViewRow-objektet er en alternativ rad <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollens. | | `Edit`| GridViewRow-objektet er i redigeringsmodus. | | `Normal`| GridViewRow-objektet er i tilstanden normal (standard). | | `Selected`| GridViewRow-objekt er valgt. | Bruk til å fastslå statusen for en GridViewRow-objektet i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.RowState%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.RowState%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control stores all of its data rows in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Rows%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll lagrer alle dataradene i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Rows%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Rows%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: To determine the index of a GridViewRow object in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Rows%2A> collection, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.RowIndex%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Å finne ut indeksen for et GridViewRow objekt i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Rows%2A>samlingen, bruker du <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.RowIndex%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.RowIndex%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Rows%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can access the properties of the underlying data object that is bound to the GridViewRow object by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.DataItem%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til egenskapene for det underliggende dataobjektet som er bundet til GridViewRow-objektet ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.DataItem%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.DataItem%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.DataItem%2A> property is available only during and after the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.RowDataBound> event of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.DataItem%2A>egenskapen er tilgjengelig bare under og etter den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.RowDataBound>hendelse for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.RowDataBound> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.DataItem%2A>

trans-unit.source: To determine the index of the data object in the underlying data source, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.DataItemIndex%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil finne indeksen for dataobjektet i den underliggende datakilden, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.DataItemIndex%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridViewRow.DataItemIndex%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can access the individual cells of the GridViewRow object by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.Cells%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til de individuelle cellene i GridViewRow-objektet ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.Cells%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.Cells%2A>

trans-unit.source: If a cell contains other controls, you can retrieve a control from the cell by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A> collection of the cell.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en celle inneholder andre kontroller, kan du hente en kontroll fra cellen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A>samling av cellen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.FindControl%2A> method of the cell to find the control, if the control has an <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A> specified.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.FindControl%2A>metode for celle for å finne kontrollen, hvis kontrollen har en <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>angitte.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.FindControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: To retrieve a field value from a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BoundField> field column or an automatically generated field column, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.Text%2A> property of the cell.
trans-unit.target: Til å hente en verdi for feltet fra en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BoundField>feltet kolonne eller en automatisk generert feltet, brukes den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.Text%2A>-egenskapen til cellen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.Text%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BoundField>

trans-unit.source: To retrieve a field value from other field column types where the field value is bound to a control, first retrieve the control from the appropriate cell and then access the appropriate property of the control.
trans-unit.target: For å hente en verdi for feltet fra andre kolonnetyper der verdien i feltet er bundet til en kontroll, hente først kontrollen fra en celle, og deretter bruker riktig-egenskapen for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > It is possible to use a data-binding expression directly in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplateField> field column without binding the value to a property of a control.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Det er mulig å bruke en databinding uttrykk som er direkte i et <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplateField>field-kolonnen uten å binde verdien til en egenskap for en kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplateField>

trans-unit.source: In this case, the field value is automatically placed in a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataBoundLiteralControl> control.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet feltverdien automatisk er plassert i en <xref:System.Web.UI.DataBoundLiteralControl>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataBoundLiteralControl>

trans-unit.source: To retrieve the field value, you must first retrieve the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataBoundLiteralControl> control from the appropriate cell and then use its <xref:System.Web.UI.DataBoundLiteralControl.Text%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: For å hente feltverdien, må du først hente den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataBoundLiteralControl>kontrollere fra en celle, og deretter bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataBoundLiteralControl.Text%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataBoundLiteralControl.Text%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataBoundLiteralControl>
